@pooja_raghu you make our new collection shine even brighter! 

Sculptors see the art within the stone before they sculpt - it’s already there, waiting to be revealed ✨

Carry art with you, wherever life takes you. 

Our limited-edition Art in Our Lives collection is a reminder to pause, observe, and find beauty in the everyday, whether in the curve of a tree, the texture of a rock, or the rhythm of nature itself. 

Each piece is a tribute to art as a timeless presence in our lives — past, present, and future.

latestPosts.caption:
Inspired by the world around us — from graceful silhouettes of women to divine deities, brass sculptures are symbols of pride and heritage passed down through generations.

Our new Art in Our Lives collection transforms these artistic traditions into something you can carry with you every day — designed by the artists at Hidesign, handcrafted by our artisans, and carried by you.

#hidesign #newcollection

Carry Art with you where ever you go ✨

The Art Collection stands out for its exquisite brass work, where every detail is treated like a miniature sculpture. The design team hand-moulded every brass element, ensuring it felt like an artwork in itself, before working with our brass foundry to bring the designs to life as complete sculptures.
